like that, verbatim, sure.

527
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:13,070
Look, I'm really sorry
that I forced this

528
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:15,720
whole reunion on you.
I think our family might be

529
00:18:15,770 --> 00:18:17,160
