My dad is just a selfish dick.

532
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:25,120
And I was too.

533
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:28,090
All the other Peralta dads,
we probably just learned it

534
00:18:28,130 --> 00:18:30,390
