the human centipede.

562
00:19:28,230 --> 00:19:29,880
- Because we have
our heads up our asses.

563
00:19:29,930 --> 00:19:32,020
Yes, we've heard that before.
- I never thought I'd say this,

564
00:19:32,060 --> 00:19:33,320
but you guys did
the right thing.

565
00:19:33,370 --> 00:19:35,020
