not to put him in your band.

595
00:20:35,690 --> 00:20:37,910
- Thank you, Captain.
Lieutenant?

596
00:20:37,950 --> 00:20:39,170
What instrument do you play?

597
00:20:39,210 --> 00:20:40,470
- The flute.
- You're hired.

598
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,090
- What?
I haven't even played.

599
00:20:42,130 --> 00:20:43,570
- You're the only flute
who auditioned.

600
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:44,570
Welcome to the band.

601
00:20:44,610 --> 00:20:46,390
- Yes!
